sections.heading: Repealed.Section 59A-14A-2 - Repealed.
sections.text:
History:Laws 2011, ch. 156, § 1; repealed by Laws 2017, ch. 130, § 19.

Repeals.— Laws 2017, ch. 130, § 19 repealed 59A-14A-1 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 2011, ch. 156, § 1, relating to the Surplus Lines Insurance Multistate Compliance Compact, entered into, effective July 1, 2017. For provisions of former section,seethe 2016 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
